{"type": "article", "id": 26636, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-11T06:44:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27448, "name": "Evoke"}, {"id": 27449, "name": "AutoCAT"}, {"id": 27450, "name": "多点"}, {"id": 27451, "name": "杭州尤皿家居设计有限公司"}, {"id": 27452, "name": "Yicong Lu"}, {"id": 27453, "name": "Sarah-Linda Forre"}, {"id": 27454, "name": "Jonathan Radetz"}, {"id": 27455, "name": "Bryan Wong"}, {"id": 27456, "name": "Chengtao Yi"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016070214544291qO7pK8Eow6NJmC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Bread lamp by Yicong Lu</h2>\n<p class=\"\">谁说面包不能成为灯具的灵感来源？设计师 Yicong Lu 的这款“面包灯”看上去就像是一个烤面包机，插槽中的“面包片”充当了灯泡的角色。虽然并没有设计专门的调光器，但只要上下调整“面包片”的高度即可改变灯光的亮度，既生动又充满了科技感。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180857TQwfWFkC0ygE2p6I.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180857zPIJtQ13608M45NY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180858pmqoADc3uGBTY1eP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180858zwGBb31oPTnC5eSa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180859fcty01bjX9qrIkQh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Evoke by Sarah-Linda Forre</h2>\n<p class=\"\">第一眼看到 Evoke 系列餐具，你也许很容易联想到原始社会的人们用贝壳制作的工具。设计师 <a href=\"http://www.sarahlindaforrer.com/\">Sarah-Linda Forre</a> 希望通过这些看起来非常原生态的器具，挑战用刀叉的传统用餐方式，激起人们对于食物的思考。目前这套餐具还处于开发阶段，你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.voordekunst.nl/projecten/4449-evoke-een-collectie-eetgereedschap-1\">链接</a>参与众筹。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180859KDM26XgAS43LQkrT.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5806846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180859vAYysU9L5g2SiRfj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180900vTzs84UemZLKSraB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180900mTbwEQgZ37Go2MXN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56234719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180901jmHebR6koVl7Jgh9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.92298289\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071809011PZTKSAxLebaBF2p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Seismograph vase by Jonathan Radetz</h2>\n<p class=\"\">从大自然中汲取设计灵感并不是件新鲜事，将灾难通过美学呈现就不多见了。设计师 Jonathan Radetz 根据地震仪记录下的图像，制作了被命名为 Italy 和 New Zealand 的两款<a href=\"http://dua-collection.com/en/collection/seismographic-vases\">花瓶</a>。他的这个创意在不久前还赢得了 2016 年德国设计奖，<a href=\"http://www.dua-shop.de/en/shop/home-accessories/new-zealand-seismographic-vases/\">售价为 178 欧元</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180902PpgoHiqM3D19O4G0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060718090240vz3nrmWAwNSUFE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180903SHqleGNYIRytkKdb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.9975\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180903kBpHVAY5lEinsMWK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.90375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180904r3mwINfZkWQKhC4O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180904tHwduXrZ2zgPqhMx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.745\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Zirconia sharpener by Bryan Wong<b> </b>and Chengtao Yi</h2>\n<p class=\"\">这款极简风格的<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/36820783/Zirconia-Sharpener\">卷笔器</a>由 <a href=\"http://www.bryanwongdesign.com/\">Bryan Wong</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.chengtaoyi.com/\">Chengtao Yi</a> 共同设计，由一整块白色的锆石陶瓷制成。和其他卷笔器具最大的区别在于它利用锆石本身来切削铅笔，相比普通的卷笔刀在耐用程度上有了很大的提升。简洁的外形以及陶瓷的质感也是它的加分项，可惜的是目前还未开始出售。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180905yebipkAlQ0LqFP1c.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180905Gk6Qt9Pcx0NDAmUZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180906WeMpAZYi3H782Jud.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180906XnmOcygaH0jrYVDd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66748166\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180907I5yBspzgMPKv96SZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180907xFE4Hz9j1chMwWai.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>月历 by AutoCAT</h2>\n<p class=\"\">“亲爱的月历君，你想成为什么？”AutoCAT 日历设计研究中心找到的答案是：变成一座房子。这样的变身为普通的纸质月历增添了一股乐趣，让人更愿意将它们摆在桌头。透过窗户还专门标出了比较重要的日子，月份的标示则隐藏在每座房子门口。就像是俄罗斯套娃那样，这 12 座房子还可以套在一起，让你不需要担忧它们会不会太占地方。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180908qCb5mY2rgkdOjUT9.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180908B7hTQgM5p4RlNPmi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180909XsBg8FEmnJbl0P7y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180909HoW12ECIya5u6ceB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180910VYchP0Aksn4KUeIl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33384615\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180910Pg0KIT5rLStcD4Jw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>“多点” by umn-design</h2>\n<p class=\"medium-insert-images-wide\">这款开放式的香樟木收纳盒名为“多点”，由来自杭州的尤皿家居设计有限公司设计。开放式的设计让樟木芬充分散发，提升了去除异味和防霉的效果。打破条条框框的十字点则使得收纳更为随意灵活，设计时还留有细小的缝隙让木板能够在梅雨季节收缩。它目前还处于<a href=\"http://z.jd.com/project/details/50716.html\">众筹阶段</a>，最低售价为 135 元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071809109ABMIokNrayHsEbt.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180911ByqYFnOjmILXkwtv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071809119uUoMxDFwsn8fE5T.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180912F6B8t14nR5SY9LqI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180912waUp59CsDWK6YBuQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180913RvUJZdD0tEr197Ah.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}